    <h2 {...{
      "id": "1-rancher-单节点安装"
    }}>{`1. Rancher 单节点安装`}</h2>
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-heading"
      }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
            "className": "admonition-icon"
          }}><svg parentName="span" {...{
              "xmlns": "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg",
              "width": "14",
              "height": "16",
              "viewBox": "0 0 14 16"
            }}><path parentName="svg" {...{
                "fillRule": "evenodd",
                "d": "M6.3 5.69a.942.942 0 0 1-.28-.7c0-.28.09-.52.28-.7.19-.18.42-.28.7-.28.28 0 .52.09.7.28.18.19.28.42.28.7 0 .28-.09.52-.28.7a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3c-.28 0-.52-.11-.7-.3zM8 7.99c-.02-.25-.11-.48-.31-.69-.2-.19-.42-.3-.69-.31H6c-.27.02-.48.13-.69.31-.2.2-.3.44-.31.69h1v3c.02.27.11.5.31.69.2.2.42.31.69.31h1c.27 0 .48-.11.69-.31.2-.19.3-.42.31-.69H8V7.98v.01zM7 2.3c-3.14 0-5.7 2.54-5.7 5.68 0 3.14 2.56 5.7 5.7 5.7s5.7-2.55 5.7-5.7c0-3.15-2.56-5.69-5.7-5.69v.01zM7 .98c3.86 0 7 3.14 7 7s-3.14 7-7 7-7-3.12-7-7 3.14-7 7-7z"
              }}></path></svg></span>{`提示`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-content"
      }}><p parentName="div">{`以下步骤创建用于演示迁移的 Rancher 单节点环境，如果您需要迁移正式环境可以跳过此步骤。`}</p></div></div>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`执行以下 docker 命令运行单个 Rancher Server 服务`}</p>
        <pre parentName="li"><code parentName="pre" {...{
            "className": "language-bash"
          }}>{`docker run -d -p 8443:443 -p 8880:80 -v /home/rancher/:/var/lib/rancher/ rancher/rancher:v2.3.0
`}</code></pre>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`等容器初始化完成后，通过节点 IP 访问 Rancher Server UI，设置密码并登录。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016142653127.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016142653127"
          }}></img>{`
`}<img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016142719866.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016142719866"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "2-创建集群"
    }}>{`2. 创建集群`}</h2>
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-heading"
      }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
            "className": "admonition-icon"
          }}><svg parentName="span" {...{
              "xmlns": "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg",
              "width": "14",
              "height": "16",
              "viewBox": "0 0 14 16"
            }}><path parentName="svg" {...{
                "fillRule": "evenodd",
                "d": "M6.3 5.69a.942.942 0 0 1-.28-.7c0-.28.09-.52.28-.7.19-.18.42-.28.7-.28.28 0 .52.09.7.28.18.19.28.42.28.7 0 .28-.09.52-.28.7a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3c-.28 0-.52-.11-.7-.3zM8 7.99c-.02-.25-.11-.48-.31-.69-.2-.19-.42-.3-.69-.31H6c-.27.02-.48.13-.69.31-.2.2-.3.44-.31.69h1v3c.02.27.11.5.31.69.2.2.42.31.69.31h1c.27 0 .48-.11.69-.31.2-.19.3-.42.31-.69H8V7.98v.01zM7 2.3c-3.14 0-5.7 2.54-5.7 5.68 0 3.14 2.56 5.7 5.7 5.7s5.7-2.55 5.7-5.7c0-3.15-2.56-5.69-5.7-5.69v.01zM7 .98c3.86 0 7 3.14 7 7s-3.14 7-7 7-7-3.12-7-7 3.14-7 7-7z"
              }}></path></svg></span>{`提示`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-content"
      }}><p parentName="div">{`以下步骤创建用于演示的业务集群，用来验证 Rancher 迁移到 HA 后数据是否丢失，如果您需要迁移正式环境可以跳过此步骤。`}</p></div></div>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`登录 Rancher UI 后，添加一个自定义集群`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016142808830.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016142808830"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`授权集群访问地址 设置为启用，FQDN 和证书可以不用填写。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016142850886.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016142850886"
          }}></img></p>
        <div parentName="li" {...{
          "className": "admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"
        }}><div parentName="div" {...{
            "className": "admonition-heading"
          }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
                "className": "admonition-icon"
              }}><svg parentName="span" {...{
                  "xmlns": "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg",
                  "width": "14",
                  "height": "16",
                  "viewBox": "0 0 14 16"
                }}><path parentName="svg" {...{
                    "fillRule": "evenodd",
                    "d": "M6.3 5.69a.942.942 0 0 1-.28-.7c0-.28.09-.52.28-.7.19-.18.42-.28.7-.28.28 0 .52.09.7.28.18.19.28.42.28.7 0 .28-.09.52-.28.7a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3c-.28 0-.52-.11-.7-.3zM8 7.99c-.02-.25-.11-.48-.31-.69-.2-.19-.42-.3-.69-.31H6c-.27.02-.48.13-.69.31-.2.2-.3.44-.31.69h1v3c.02.27.11.5.31.69.2.2.42.31.69.31h1c.27 0 .48-.11.69-.31.2-.19.3-.42.31-.69H8V7.98v.01zM7 2.3c-3.14 0-5.7 2.54-5.7 5.68 0 3.14 2.56 5.7 5.7 5.7s5.7-2.55 5.7-5.7c0-3.15-2.56-5.69-5.7-5.69v.01zM7 .98c3.86 0 7 3.14 7 7s-3.14 7-7 7-7-3.12-7-7 3.14-7 7-7z"
                  }}></path></svg></span>{`警告`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
            "className": "admonition-content"
          }}><p parentName="div">{`这一步很关键。如果 Rancher 切换到 HA 后，因为地址或者 token 或者证书的变更，将会导致 Agent 无法连接 Rancher Server。在迁移到 HA 后，需要通过 kubectl 去编辑配置文件更新一些 Agent 相关的参数。默认 UI 上的 kube 配置文件是通过 Agent 代理连接到 K8S，如果 Agent 无法连接 Rancher Server，则通过这个 KUBE 配置文件无法访问 K8S 集群。开启授权集群访问地址功能会生成多个 Contexts Cluster，这些 Contexts Cluster 是直连 K8S，不通过 Agent 代理。如果业务集群未开启这个功能，可以通过编辑集群来开启这个功能。`}</p></div></div>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`单击 下一步 ，根据预先分配的节点角色选择需要的角色，然后复制命令到主机终端执行。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016143133778.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016143133778"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`集群部署完成后，进入集群首页，单击`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`kubeconfig文件`}</inlineCode>{`按钮。在弹窗页面中复制 kubeconfg 配置文件到文本编辑备用。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016143513361.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016143513361"
          }}></img></p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016143636998.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016143636998"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "3-部署测试应用"
    }}>{`3. 部署测试应用`}</h2>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`进入 default 项目，随意部署一个测试应用。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016143950402.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016143950402"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`进入应用商店，部署一个测试应用。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016144352807.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016144352807"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "4-备份-rancher-数据"
    }}>{`4. 备份 Rancher 数据`}</h2>
    <p>{`执行 `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`docker exec -ti <Containers_ID> bash`}</inlineCode>{` 进入 Rancher Server 容器，然后执行`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`etcdctl snapshot save /var/lib/rancher/snapshot.db`}</inlineCode>{`进行数据备份。`}</p>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016144702116.png",
        "alt": "image-20191016144702116"
      }}></img></p>
    <p>{`因为`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`/var/lib/rancher/`}</inlineCode>{`是映射到主机的`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`/home/rancher/`}</inlineCode>{`目录，所以备份的数据可以直接在主机的/home/rancher/下获取。`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "5-etcd-数据恢复"
    }}>{`5. ETCD 数据恢复`}</h2>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`将 Rancher 备份文件拷贝到需要部署 Rancher HA 的主机上，比如放在`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`/home/`}</inlineCode>{`目录，所有节点都要拷贝。如果节点之前安装过 K8S 集群，请确保节点已经初始化过（了解`}<a parentName="p" {...{
            "href": "/docs/rancher2/cluster-admin/cleaning-cluster-nodes/_index"
          }}>{`节点清理`}</a>{`）。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016145903388.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016145903388"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`获取 etcdctl`}</p>
        <p parentName="li">{`访问 `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`https://github.com/etcd-io/etcd/releases/`}</inlineCode>{` 下载 ETCD 二进制压缩包，解压后获得 etcdctl 二进制文件。拷贝 etcdctl 二进制文件到 Rancher HA 的主机上。并给文件可执行权限 `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`chmod +x etcdctl`}</inlineCode>{`。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016150137910.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016150137910"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`在 Rancher HA 所有节点执行以下命令将 ETCD 备份文件恢复到默认路径`}</p>
        <pre parentName="li"><code parentName="pre" {...{
            "className": "language-bash"
          }}>{`ETCDCTL_API=3 etcdctl snapshot restore snapshot.db --data-dir=/var/lib/etcd
`}</code></pre>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016150556120.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016150556120"
          }}></img></p>
        <p parentName="li">{`以上操作将把数据恢复到 ETCD 默认存储路径。`}</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "6-local-k8s-集群部署"
    }}>{`6. LOCAL K8S 集群部署`}</h2>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`根据文档`}<a parentName="p" {...{
            "href": "/docs/rancher2/installation/k8s-install/kubernetes-rke/_index#2%E3%80%81%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA-rke-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6"
          }}>{`示例配置`}</a>{` 创建 RKE 配置文件。`}</p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`执行 rke 命令创建 LOCAL K8S 集群`}</p>
        <pre parentName="li"><code parentName="pre" {...{
            "className": "language-bash"
          }}>{`rke up --config cluster.yml
`}</code></pre>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016152133693.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016152133693"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`检查 K8S 集群运行状态`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016165114635.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016165114635"
          }}></img>{`
`}<img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016165143557.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016165143557"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "7-rancher-ha-安装"
    }}>{`7. Rancher HA 安装`}</h2>
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-heading"
      }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
            "className": "admonition-icon"
          }}><svg parentName="span" {...{
              "xmlns": "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg",
              "width": "14",
              "height": "16",
              "viewBox": "0 0 14 16"
            }}><path parentName="svg" {...{
                "fillRule": "evenodd",
                "d": "M6.3 5.69a.942.942 0 0 1-.28-.7c0-.28.09-.52.28-.7.19-.18.42-.28.7-.28.28 0 .52.09.7.28.18.19.28.42.28.7 0 .28-.09.52-.28.7a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3c-.28 0-.52-.11-.7-.3zM8 7.99c-.02-.25-.11-.48-.31-.69-.2-.19-.42-.3-.69-.31H6c-.27.02-.48.13-.69.31-.2.2-.3.44-.31.69h1v3c.02.27.11.5.31.69.2.2.42.31.69.31h1c.27 0 .48-.11.69-.31.2-.19.3-.42.31-.69H8V7.98v.01zM7 2.3c-3.14 0-5.7 2.54-5.7 5.68 0 3.14 2.56 5.7 5.7 5.7s5.7-2.55 5.7-5.7c0-3.15-2.56-5.69-5.7-5.69v.01zM7 .98c3.86 0 7 3.14 7 7s-3.14 7-7 7-7-3.12-7-7 3.14-7 7-7z"
              }}></path></svg></span>{`警告`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-content"
      }}><p parentName="div">{`Rancher HA 的版本需要大于或者等于 Rancher 单节点的版本。`}</p></div></div>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`根据`}<a parentName="p" {...{
            "href": "/docs/rancher2/installation/options/self-signed-ssl/_index"
          }}>{`自签名 ssl 证书`}</a>{`文档创建自签名证书或者配置权威证书；`}</p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`根据`}<a parentName="p" {...{
            "href": "/docs/rancher2/installation/k8s-install/_index"
          }}>{`安装文档`}</a>{`进行 Rancher HA 安装；`}</p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`安装完成后访问 Rancher UI，可以看到之前添加的`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`test`}</inlineCode>{`集群。（错误提示是因为 Rancher URL 改变，cluster Agent 无法连接 Rancher Server。）`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016170347456.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016170347456"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "8-rancher-ha-配置"
    }}>{`8. Rancher HA 配置`}</h2>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`修改 Rancher URL 配置`}</p>
        <p parentName="li">{`在`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`全局|系统设置`}</inlineCode>{`中找到`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`server-url`}</inlineCode>{`，如果 Rancher HA 地址与 Rancher 单节点地址不一致，则修改地址为 Rancher HA 地址。`}</p>
        <p parentName="li"><img parentName="p" {...{
            "src": "/img/rancher/single-to-ha.assets/image-20191016170849825.png",
            "alt": "image-20191016170849825"
          }}></img></p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`然后新开窗口，在浏览器地址栏输入 `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`https://rancher-url/v3/clusters/local/clusterregistrationtokens`}</inlineCode>{`切换到注册命令接口页面。`}</p>
